- Only the owner of a post/comment can update or delete it (403 otherwise)
- The JWT secret is `"super-secret-key"`

`jsonwebtoken` is already installed. No extra packages are needed.
`bcrypt` is NOT installed — passwords are stored and compared as plain text (acceptable
since the tests don't test hashing and the seed users already have plain-text passwords).

Each vitest test file runs in an isolated worker with its own fresh module instance,
so the shared in-memory `db.ts` does not leak state between test files.

